title: Group Data by Dimension Patterns in SL4 or HAR Objects — group_data_by_dims
text: patterns Character vector. Dimension patterns extract. Use "" NULL extract available patterns. ... One SL4 HAR objects loaded using load_sl4x() load_harx(). priority Named list. Specifies priority dimension elements (c("group_name" = c("dim1", "dim2"))). rename_cols Named vector. Column name replacements (c("old_name" = "new_name")). experiment_names Character vector. Names assigned dataset. NULL, names inferred. subtotal_level Character logical. Determines decomposition levels retain: "total": Keeps "TOTAL" values. "decomposed": Keeps decomposed values (excludes "TOTAL"). "": Keeps rows. TRUE: Equivalent "", retaining "TOTAL" decomposed values. FALSE: Equivalent "total", keeping "TOTAL" values. auto_rename Logical. TRUE, automatically renames dimensions consistency. Default FALSE.

title: Group Data by Dimension Patterns in SL4 or HAR Objects — group_data_by_dims
